&lt;p data-start=&quot;1347&quot; data-end=&quot;1467&quot;&gt;Generate and integrate &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1370&quot; data-end=&quot;1381&quot;&gt;DFT RTL&lt;/strong&gt;, ensuring quality through RTL-level checks (e.g., linting and DFT rule verification).&lt;/p&gt;
